				<wikidot:authorName>Doctor North</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4695462</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The rules of cricket<br /> You have two sides</p> <p>One out in the field and one in.</p> <p>Each man that’s on the teams that’s in, goes out. And when he out he comes in, and the next man comes in till he’s out.</p> <p>When they’re all out the side that was out comes in. the side that in goes out and tries to get those coming in, out. and sometimes you have men that in but not out.</p> <p>When both sides have been in and out including the not outs that’s the end of the game.﻿</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
